    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate CFD model correctly identifies worst-case hemolysis operating condition with RH = 0.87 < 1.0 acceptance criterion. Discretization error well-characterized (GCI < 3%). Aleatory uncertainty from blood rheological variability and inter-donor variation was noted qualitatively across validation activities; structured UQ characterization was not completed for all validation results but is acceptable at MRL 2 given medium model influence and availability of experimental confirmation. Overall credibility sufficient to support regulatory submission for Class II device.",
